title: DDFP: Andrew Luck interview
itunes:title: DDFP: Andrew Luck interview
description:
Listen to Shek's 1-on-1 interview with Colts quarterback Andrew Luck during the offseason. Luck joined the show courtesy of Quaker and discussed his favorite quarterbacks to watch, which young QB has the most speed, and his famous beard.
